com.scalar.db.sql.springdata

Class ScalarDbJdbcAggregateTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.data.jdbc.core.JdbcAggregateTemplate
      • com.scalar.db.sql.springdata.ScalarDbJdbcAggregateTemplate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.data.jdbc.core.JdbcAggregateOperations

    public class ScalarDbJdbcAggregateTemplate
extends org.springframework.data.jdbc.core.JdbcAggregateTemplate
    An extended $JdbcAggregateTemplate customized for ScalarDB SQL. This prevents users from using some APIs that are not supported in ScalarDB by throwing $UnsupportedOperationException.
